"Melbourne’s rebellion closed with a ‘Festival of Love and Rage’. Rebels "
"disrupted the city by land and sea, with street theatre, a flotilla of "
"canoes on the Yarra River, a bike parade, and a roadblock. 9 festival goers "
"were arrested for their efforts."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-01-12-global-newsletter-47.md:182
